---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Us | Beyond Visual Optometry | Xinzhuang & Banqiao, New Taipei"
  description="Beyond Visual Optometry — a high-trust clinical optometry brand in New Taipei City. Founded in Banqiao in 1992. Led by licensed optometrist YoYo Cheng."
  lang="en"
  enPath="/en/about"
>
  <section class="bg-brand-navy text-white py-20 px-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-white mb-4" style="font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,48px);font-weight:300">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-white/70 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto font-sans">Not the most expensive — just the most suitable. That's our promise.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Brand story -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 py-20" style="background:#f7f3ec">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="font-sans text-brand-gold mb-4" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.2em">OUR STORY</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-brand-ink mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,34px);font-weight:300">30+ Years in New Taipei City</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-brand-ink-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <p>Beyond Visual Optometry began in Banqiao in 1992. Over three decades, we have served thousands of families in New Taipei City — from children getting their first glasses to seniors navigating progressive lenses.</p>
            <p>In 2023, we expanded to Xinzhuang, partnering with BiYang Optometry Clinic to bring the same clinical-grade standard to the area near Fu Jen Catholic University.</p>
            <p>We are not a fast-fashion optical chain. Every customer receives a full clinical exam, personalized lens recommendation, and ongoing follow-up care.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-navy/5 border border-brand-ink/10 p-8">
          <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-sm">
            {[
              { label: 'Founded', value: '1992, Banqiao' },
              { label: 'Locations', value: 'Xinzhuang × BiYang Optometry\nBanqiao × Neng Jian Du Optometry' },
              { label: 'ZEISS Partnership', value: 'Authorized certified dealer' },
              { label: 'Google Rating', value: '5.0 ★ (Xinzhuang: 221 reviews\nBanqiao: 47 reviews)' },
              { label: 'Exam Duration', value: '45–60 minutes (full clinical exam)' },
            ].map(item => (
              <div class="border-b border-brand-ink/10 pb-4">
                <p class="text-brand-gold text-xs mb-1" style="letter-spacing:0.1em">{item.label.toUpperCase()}</p>
                <p class="text-brand-ink whitespace-pre-line">{item.value}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- YoYo -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-16 py-20" style="background:#eee8da">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-sans text-brand-gold mb-4 text-center" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.2em">LEAD OPTOMETRIST</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-brand-ink mb-12 text-center" style="font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,34px);font-weight:300">YoYo Cheng</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-brand-ink-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>YoYo (Cheng Chia-Yu) is a licensed optometrist (License No. 003309) and the lead clinician at Beyond Visual Optometry's Xinzhuang location.</p>
          <p>Her approach is rooted in the belief that a proper eye exam takes time. Every consultation includes full binocular vision assessment, accommodation testing, and personalized lens planning — not just a quick prescription check.</p>
          <p>She specializes in progressive lens adaptation, high myopia precision fitting, children's myopia tracking, and digital eye strain management.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 font-sans text-sm">
          {[
            { label: 'License', value: 'Optometrist License No. 003309' },
            { label: 'Clinic License', value: 'New Taipei City BiYang Optometry\nNo. 5Y31060655' },
            { label: 'Specialties', value: 'Progressive lens fitting\nHigh myopia precision glasses\nChildren\'s myopia tracking\nBinocular vision assessment\nDigital eye strain' },
            { label: 'Language', value: 'Mandarin Chinese (primary)\nBasic English communication available' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="bg-white border border-brand-ink/10 p-4">
              <p class="text-brand-gold text-xs mb-1" style="letter-spacing:0.1em">{item.label.toUpperCase()}</p>
              <p class="text-brand-ink whitespace-pre-line">{item.value}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 text-center" style="background:#f7f3ec">
    <a href="/en/booking" class="font-sans bg-brand-navy text-white px-10 py-4 hover:bg-brand-navy/90 transition-colors" style="font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.1em">Book an Exam</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
